basic.floral_language:
Lonicera nitida
Floriography: pure, honest, selfless
Can be used for herbal tea. The flower buds are like rods before opening, after opened, they are like trumpets, initially in white color, gradually turn yellow in 1-2 days, with slight sweet fragrance. the stamens and style are extending beyond the petals, look glamorous.
Likes gentle sunshine, tolerates to half shade, can be place under bright scattered light, flowering in March-June for 3-4 weeks.
basic.blooming: Flowering period March-June, viewing period 3-4 weeks
basic.color: Flower color white at the beginning, then yellow, with fragrance
